parameters:
\n< Demuran >Hey, hey, esteemed members of the patrol team.
Thank you for your hard work and efforts today
despite being busy.

\n< Demuran >It's neither hot nor cold, a truly perfect day for
investigation.

\n<Patrol Team>...With our hands in the dark like this, it
doesn't seem like the investigation will progress.

\n< Demuran >Well, we have prepared a special dog on our end.
It seems that the night would be more convenient
for various reasons.
\n< Demuran >How is it? Isn't it splendid?

\n< Demuran >This one has a good sense of smell. Well, maybe a
bit too good. It's not very friendly and training
it was quite difficult.

\n< Demuran >Finally, huh. Our love has reached her, or should
I say, she has been made aware of her place.

\n< Demuran >In that case, I thought her sharp sense of smell
might come in handy for this investigation. Yes.

\n< Demuran >With your proud sense of smell that sticks its
nose into everything, you'll lead us to solve this
case, won't you? Right, Nicola?

\n< Demuran >Kukuku! Look, as you can see, this one is quite
faithful, you know!

\n<City Police>We're taking care of her from morning till night,
everyone in the squad!

\n< Serena >The despicable acts of someone who doesn't even
see others as human...

\n< Serena >Know that your wicked deeds will come to an end
today!
\n< Demuran >Oh? If it isn't the little toilet bowl.
\n< Demuran >I thought you would bring one or two helpers.

\n<City Police>Look who's talking, you brat. The patrol team is
cornered, aren't they?

\n< Demuran >Kukuku. Well, if you're looking for a fight, I
wouldn't mind giving it to you.

\n< Demuran >You understand, right? It means that you were the
one who made the first move.

\n< Demuran >Last time, I didn't want to make it public. I let
you off with just a light punishment...

\n< Demuran >This time, I'll be a criminal without any
restrictions.
\n< Demuran >Prepare yourself for the end of your life.
\n< Serena >No matter what, I will annihilate you all!
\n<Patrol Team>Everyone, let's do it! Let's retrieve our captain!
ーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーー
ーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーー
